        </h4>
        <p>
          Hey, my name is Mathew Cohen and I am MaCo
          <span class="em">[may-koh]</span> Guitars.
        </p>
        <p>
          While I have 20+ years combined experience as a touring musician and
          recording engineer, I've also been a maker of things for much of my
          life but I did not start building my own guitars until 2018.
          <strong>Weird, right?</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          My shop is located in the beautiful Greater Seattle Area and I use the
          best domestic and exotic woods and materials I can get my hands on to
          build one of a kind instruments. I make a very limited number of
          instruments per year so I can focus on creating one of a kind
          instruments that do not leave my shop without meeting my high
          standards.
        </p>
        <p>
          In short, I make custom guitars and basses and I'd like to make one
          (or more) for you... because let's face it - if you really love a
          guitar, it just sounds better.
        </p>
